		"name": "HRM SaaS Collection - COMPLETE",
		"description": "# HRM SaaS MVP API Documentation\n\nSelamat datang di dokumentasi API untuk sistem **Multi-tenant HRM SaaS**. Dokumentasi ini mencakup seluruh fitur inti yang dibutuhkan untuk fase MVP.\n\n## Fitur Utama\n1.  **Multi-tenancy**: Data antar perusahaan terisolasi sepenuhnya (Tenant isolation).\n2.  **Authentication**: Menggunakan Laravel Sanctum (Bearer Token).\n3.  **Attendance**: Absensi berbasis lokasi (Geo-tagging) dengan deteksi keterlambatan otomatis berdasarkan jadwal.\n4.  **Work Schedules & Shifts**: Pengaturan jam kerja fleksibel (Pagi, Sore, Malam, NOC).\n5.  **Leave & Reimbursement**: Alur pengajuan dan persetujuan (Approval workflow).\n6.  **Payroll & Slip Gaji**: (Coming Soon).\n7.  **Reporting**: Export data absensi ke format Excel.\n\n## Role System\n-   **Super Admin**: Akses penuh ke seluruh sistem.\n-   **HRD / Manager**: Mengelola karyawan, jadwal, dan menyetujui pengajuan di dalam satu perusahaan.\n-   **Employee**: Melakukan absensi, melihat riwayat, dan mengajukan cuti/klaim.\n\n## Persiapan Penggunaan\n1.  Pastikan **Environment** `HRM SaaS Env` sudah terpilih.\n2.  Variabel `base_url` harus mengarah ke backend Anda (default: `http://127.0.0.1:8000`).\n3.  Lakukan **Login** terlebih dahulu. Token akan otomatis tersimpan ke variabel `token` setelah login berhasil.\n\n---\n*Dibuat oleh Ahmad Rizki - PT. Artacomindo Jejaring Nusa - 2026*",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Authentication",
			"description": "Endpoints for Login, Logout, and User profile.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.access_token) {",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.data.access_token);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"superadmin@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password\"\n}",
							"options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
						},
						"url": "{{base_url}}/api/login"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Logout",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
						],
						"url": "{{base_url}}/api/logout"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Current User",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
						],
						"url": "{{base_url}}/api/user"
					}
				}
			]
		},
